      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我发现客户忠诚度还回连到了订单管理，形成闭环。这样画出来会有一条从D回到A的线，确认保留吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_CustomerLoyalty",
        "Retail_OrderManagement"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "保留，这是反馈链路。客户积分变动要回流更新订单状态。现在把库存系统加进来，放在POS下游。",
      "elements_involved": [
